== JR Test Suite

JR Test suite is an testing application for JR. You'll need to make sure you have JR installed and it is reference properly in your Gemfile

== Caveats 

JR currently only supports Thin server. Thus, be sure to run your server with:

  rails s thin 

== Running the Demo

Start the test server and jump on over to /demo/index. Pull up more browsers and see your changes propagate. 

== Running Test Cases

We use Jasmine to test our javascript. Jump over to /test to start the tests. 

== About

JR Test Suite is a Pearl Street Labs project. 